Hi <@UGY6JNTB4> , I have installed the HubSpot plugin on my wordpress site. I want to hide the widget by default and display it when someone clicks the help menu.
```window.HubSpotConversations.widget.remove();
jQuery('.help-menu').on("click", function () {   window.HubSpotConversations.widget.load({ widgetOpen: true });
});```
